    <p><br/></p>

    <h5>Breathing Orange</h5>
    <p>
        Gain access to your Mr Beam II via <a href="http://find.mr-beam.org" target="_blank">find.mr-beam.org</a>.
    </p>

    <h5>Breathing Green</h5>
    <p>
        Gain access to your Mr Beam II via the WiFi Access Point.
    </p>
